  <h2>Benefits of Simply Delicious Meal Plans</h2>

  <h4>Time Savings are HUGE!</h4>
  <p>
  What's your time worth? For less than 15 cents a day eliminate endless trips to the supermarket, searching recipes, making shopping lists, formulating a plan to tackle the daily dilemma of what to feed the family for dinner. Spend no more time eating out than you want to--AND the Chef has created simply delicious recipes, so you save time in preparation. <span style="color: #404040; font-weight: bold;">No more meal planning, more time in your day.</span>
  </p>

  <h4>Better Nutrition!</h4>

  <p>
  With a plan you can be sure that you're eating a variety of foods - one of the keys to good nutrition. The Chef has thoughtfully chosen different meats, veggies, and fruits to enjoy in a week's time, and limited the number of highly processed foods, so preparing Everything but the Chef meals on a regular basis beats eating out, or eating out of a box.
  </p>

  <h4>Variety!</h4>

  <p>
  Ever get tired of a weekly regimen of spaghetti, pizza, tacos, burgers---repeat? Do you have 6-12 or more months of recipes for delicious main courses with satisfying side dishes? <span style="color: #404040; font-weight: bold;">Give Chef a try; you'll be surprised at all the different things you can make simply at home.</span>
  </p>

  <h4>Save Money!</h4>
  <p>
  Experts have pointed out the fact that having a - plan - before you do your shopping is the single most cost effective thing you can do to save money on groceries. But pre-planning meals and then making out shopping lists and checking for needed ingredients, etc. takes time. What's your time worth? For less than 15 cents a day eliminate your pre-planning, and use our plan to help you cut down on endless trips to the supermarket, keep your shopping focused to avoid impulse buying which cuts down on buying food you don't really need and buying food that will go bad before you ever use it. Plus no more need to eat out so often. All this saves you money on gas, groceries and expensive prepared food.
  </p>

